                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17950218-17-defend211 t17950218-17-punish85"></join>
               Publickly whipped
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
